{
  "chapter": 56,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十七回\"众叛亲离\"。裴珏与\"七巧童子\"吴鸣世、袁泸珍在酒楼上观战。街面上，\"神手\"战飞当众出示证人\"过不去\"，指控\"龙形八掌\"檀明十余年前在保定城杀害\"枪剑无敌\"裴氏双杰。檀明矢口否认，双方陷入僵持。关键时刻，檀明四大亲信——\"八卦掌\"柳辉、\"快马神刀\"龚清洋、\"摄魂刀\"罗义、边少衍——集体反水。柳辉揭露檀明做贼心虚、图谋消灭\"江南同盟\"，并抛出关键证据：当年裴氏双杰所护之宝\"碧玉蟾蜍\"此刻就在檀明身上。罗义更道出碧玉蟾蜍与自己义兄\"断魂刀\"孙斌的渊源。人群激愤要求搜身，檀明宁死不从，拔掌击退罗义，众叛亲离之下抱定必死之心。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "此时此刻，还有什么好笑的事么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "七巧童子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我在笑这些少年得志的少年，凭着父兄师门的余荫，在武林中博得了一份声名，却丝毫不知道武林中的奸诈，'龙形八掌'眼见已是众叛亲离，穷途日暮，这东方铁竟还在为他说话……唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "惟其如此，我才觉得东方兄弟毕竟不失为名门之后，热血男儿，你怎能如此轻蔑他们？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "战庄主可是有什么真实的证据么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "你可是真的要证据？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拿证据来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_guo_bu_qu",
      "text": "过不去，你可认得此人是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "过不去",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "这位就是'龙形八掌'檀大爷！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_guo_bu_qu",
      "text": "你且站在这里，将你亲眼所见之事，当着天下英雄说出来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_bu_qu",
      "speaker_name": "过不去",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "小……小人……不……敢……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "东方少堡主可愿负责此人的安全？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "在下以身家名誉为保，此人若有半分损伤，惟我东方铁是问！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_guo_bu_qu",
      "text": "有了东方少堡主保护，你还不放心么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "七巧童子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "再过片刻，裴兄你便可步下楼去，为亲复仇了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "我只愿无人助我。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "袁泸珍",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "我也不愿看到这么多人来围殴一个老人，即使……唉，即使他是我不共戴天的仇人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位朋友，你们可曾听到他的话了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀明，你还有什么话说？十余年前那大雪之夜，你可是到了保定城？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "如此说来，你已承认'枪剑无敌'裴氏双杰乃是被你毒手杀死？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "十余年前，那大雪之夜，在保定城中的人，何止千千万万，难道就全都是害死裴氏双杰的凶手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "好无耻的狡辩，难道你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "你笑些什么？哼哼，真亏你直到此刻还笑得出来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "凭着一个贩夫走卒的言语，你便说是真凭实据，老夫真不知道你是奸狡抑或是愚蠢？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "像这样的证人，老夫随时随地都可以收买数十个，各位朋友俱是明眼人，难道就信了他的话么？",
      "tone": "大声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "凭心而论，这的确算不得是真凭实据，战庄主……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "text": "好个算不得真凭实据，如此说来事隔经年，除了\"枪剑无敌\"人死复生，便再无一人，能证明这姓檀的便是杀人的凶手了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "七巧童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个狡猾的老人！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴珏",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "text": "不过以事论事，直到目前为止，我们当真没有一件真正可以定人犯罪的证据，若凭这些莫须有之事，便置人死地，当非……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "七巧童子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "裴兄，你心肠也未免太仁厚了些，妇人之仁，岂足成事？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，我兄弟虽是局外之人，但也不得不说句公道之言，若无真凭实证，还望各位三思，莫要冤枉好人！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有真凭实据！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "柳辉，你干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位朋友，我柳辉虽然跟着檀明十数年，但却还有一份良心，事到今日，我不得不说几句公道话了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "大叔暂且息怒，且听他说些什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这十余年间，檀明虽是享尽荣华，但是他亦是食不知味，睡不安稳，显然是做贼心虚，自从他听到这位赶车的朋友\"过不去\"露面之后，他就想出各种恶毒的计划，来对付'江南同盟'……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "忘恩负义的奴才！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "不可妄动！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武林之间，本已充满勾心斗角、互相欺骗之事，'飞龙镖局'与'江南同盟'势已不能并存，我要想出各种方法来将之消灭，这点我绝不否认，但谁要说我檀明就是那杀人的凶手，我檀明不惜以性命与之相拼！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "七巧童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好会做作的奸徒，想不到'龙形八掌'竟是如此角色！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "柳兄，你只管说下去，此时此刻，谅他姓檀的也不敢对你怎样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_zhan_fei",
      "text": "这些事只足以证明檀明此人的奸狡凶毒，却不能证明他便是十余年前那藏头露尾的蒙面人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但有一事，却可证明他便是杀死'枪剑无敌'裴氏双杰的凶手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位可还记得，昔年'枪剑无敌'身死那日所保的珍宝红货，是一件什么东西？有何珍贵之处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "神手",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "柳兄所说，可是那能够预知天气阴晴的异宝'碧玉蟾蜍'？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，正是'碧玉蟾蜍'，而这'碧玉蟾蜍'，此刻便是在这'龙形八掌'檀明的身上。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人群",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "搜他身上！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人群",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "叫他将'碧玉蟾蜍'拿出来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "人群",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "姓檀的，你身上若是没有'碧玉蟾蜍'，今日我们就放过你，否则我们就将你活活打死，为十余年前那些英雄的英灵复仇。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "姓檀的，你既然不是凶手，你敢让他们搜一搜身上么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "搜我……搜我身上……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢搜我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_yi",
      "speaker_name": "摄魂刀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位与这姓檀的虽有深仇大恨，但这'碧玉蟾蜍'，却是与我罗义关系最深，这一件武林隐秘，各位只怕还不知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "speaker_name": "东方湖",
      "listener": "char_luo_yi",
      "text": "兄台只管说出，在下洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_yi",
      "speaker_name": "摄魂刀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这'碧玉蟾蜍'，本是淮南一位巨商，委托我义兄，'断魂刀'孙斌护送之物，我义兄为了此物，与昔年名震江北的绿林巨盗'淮阳三煞'结下深仇，虽然刀伤追命赵老二，却被'小丧门'程英，和'夺命三郎'郑昆炎逼得无处容身，这才将'碧玉蟾蜍'转交给'枪剑无敌'护送！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_yi",
      "speaker_name": "摄魂刀",
      "listener": null,
